### 1. Create a New Resource
POST http://localhost:8080/api/countries/1/resources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Legal Guidelines for Studying Abroad",
  "description": "Important legal information for students.",
  "link": null,
  "photo": null,
  "country_id": 1
}

### 2. Create Resource with Missing Fields
POST http://localhost:8080/api/countries/1/resources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Important legal information for students."
}

### 3. Get All Resources
GET http://localhost:8080/api/countries/1/resources
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get All Resources for Non-Existing Country
GET http://localhost:8080/api/countries/999/resources
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Update an Existing Resource
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/countries/1/resources/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Legal Guidelines for Studying Abroad",
  "description": "Updated important legal information for students.",
  "link": "http://example.com",
  "photo": "http://example.com/photo.jpg",
  "country_id": 1
}

### 6. Update Non-Existing Resource
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/countries/1/resources/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Non-Existing Resource",
  "description": "This resource does not exist."
}

### 7. Delete a Resource
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/countries/1/resources/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Delete Non-Existing Resource
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/countries/1/resources/999
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Delete All Resources for a Country
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/countries/1/resources
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Get Resources After Deletion
GET http://localhost:8080/api/countries/1/resources
Content-Type: application/json
